@{B}Tool Types@{UB}


To amend a Tool Type select the Start_TD3 icon on the Workbench Screen
and select Icons/Information from the menu.

Tool Types available are
                                      OR
Driver=Your_Name
Vigilance=Isolated                    On
Time=2                                1
Speech=On                             Off
Confirm Quit=On                       Off
Intro=On                              Off
Locos_Path=TD3A:Locos/                DF0:Locos etc
Default_Loco=TD3A:Locos/87/
Routes__Path=TD3A:Routes/             DF0:Routes etc
Default_Route=TD3A:Routes/Glasgow/  * Do not use this if you want a random route
Lomem=On                              If you are short of chip memory (<1 mb) this
